A prodigious talent!

93
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,440
Is that so?

94
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,480
Absolutely true.

95
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,400
This *The Year of Celebration* script

96
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,600
is a once-in-a-century find.

97
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,720
I firmly believe once it's released,

98
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,240
it will become a cinematic classic.

99
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:44,880
Therefore,

100
