You know,

103
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,400
I actually...

104
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,400
...don't care if the project makes money.

105
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,280
What I value more

106
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,760
is the other resources

107
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,440
the film can bring me.

108
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,440
You know what I mean?

109
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,080
I understand perfectly.

110
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,440
Once this project enters the preparation phase,

111
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,520
