This is the screenwriter, Zheng Nanfeng.

114
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,040
Chairman Xu.

115
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:19,000
Truly a man of impressive appearance.

116
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:20,800
Please, have a seat.

117
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,840
I've read your script.

118
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:26,640
It's truly a rare and excellent script.

119
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:30,120
The concept of a modern person
traveling back to ancient times

120
